WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.938
RestoreAssist maintains full compliance with Australian and IICRC standards.

00:05.938 --> 00:12.891
All reports are generated in S500 format for water damage, or S520 for mould remediation.

00:12.891 --> 00:17.266
Evidence chains are tamper-evident and court-admissible.

00:17.266 --> 00:22.656
Digital signatures meet the Electronic Transactions Act requirements.

00:22.656 --> 00:27.812
Your data is stored in Australia with enterprise-grade encryption.

00:27.812 --> 00:35.469
Export audit trails, training certificates, and compliance checklists for insurers and regulators.

00:35.469 --> 00:40.000
With RestoreAssist, compliance is built in, not bolted on.